Package: stripR
Type: Package
Title: An R package to support the creation of strip maps
Version: 0.0.9999
Author: c(person("Marko", "Kallio", email = "marko.k.kallio@aalto.fi", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre"), 
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6917-7790"))
Maintainer: Marko Kallio <marko.k.kallio@aalto.fi>
Description: An R package dedicated to the processing of spatial data to support
    creation of stip maps. The package can "straigthen" arbitrary LINESTRINGs
    and rotate, move, and blend rasters along the straightened line. Functions
    are also provided for the rotation and moving of vectors along the line.
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
    sf,
    lwgeom,
    stars,
    terra,
    dplyr,
    units
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
